While researching cybercrime, I was surprised to learn how common and easy UPI fraud has become. Many people are unaware that entering a UPI PIN means money is being sent, not received, which leads to financial loss.

This task made me more aware of online threats and the importance of being cautious while using digital payment platforms. One habit I will change is that I will always verify any unknown calls or messages related to banking before taking action.

Overall, this task helped me understand how awareness and preventive measures can protect individuals from cybercrime.
